metadata.name: Visage #1
metadata.description:
"Darkened Visage" art piece #1 depicts a young woman wearing a sleek white helmet. Her face is hidden behind the helmet, giving her an anonymous and enigmatic appearance. The piece is set in a dystopian future, where helmet-wearing is the norm and individual identity is suppressed. The young woman's helmet and obscured face represent the loss of individuality and the dangers of a technology-dominated society
